<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_1c5f0af62cb1.aspx"><b>周颂·雝</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson1c5f0af62cb1">
<p>有来雝雝，至止肃肃。相维辟公，天子穆穆。於荐广牡，相予肆祀。假哉皇考！绥予孝子。</p>
<p>宣哲维人，文武维后。燕及皇天，克昌厥后。绥我眉寿，介以繁祉，既右烈考，亦右文母。</p>
</div>
